        0.3329000000        0.0143220000
        0.1043000000       -0.0034860000
H   9    1
     4570.0000000000       -0.0001390000  
      685.9000000000       -0.0010970000  
      156.5000000000       -0.0054440000  
       44.4700000000       -0.0219160000  
       14.4800000000       -0.0597510000  
